Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.98,0:01:14.36,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.50,0:01:17.45,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}穿越阴霾 来到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.87,0:01:23.38,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为守护心爱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.71,0:01:35.88,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}那一刻 齿轮悄悄转动
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.11,0:01:48.55,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}将新的命运 带到你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.08,0:01:51.56,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}恋心 生根发芽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.67,0:01:54.34,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}思念 深藏心底
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.11,0:02:02.25,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}在眼神交汇的瞬间 抛却掩饰与矜持
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.89,0:02:08.22,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}心愿只此一件 拥有坚不可摧的心灵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:14.05,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}无论在怎样的试炼中倒下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.10,0:02:16.46,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}现在 立刻 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.59,0:02:19.61,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}再一次 重新站起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.78,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}请稍带片刻
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:28.85,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}正是你赐予了我 将软弱一刀两断的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.17,0:02:33.08,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}Justice of light
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:36.18,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}静静地 静静地 扮在你身边 化身一阵微风
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.41,0:22:43.24,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只为把你沮丧的泪水  轻轻吹干
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.89,0:22:50.29,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}口袋中 那小小的愿望
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.57,0:22:57.02,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}只盼你开怀一笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.75,0:23:01.91,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}跑吧 跑吧 不断加速
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.25,0:23:05.63,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}即使发生不开心的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.79,0:23:09.03,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}也要在这条路上继续奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.29,0:23:13.94,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}前方的地图 早已印在心中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.18,0:23:17.72,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,200)}{\blur2)}明天是个 happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.43,0:23:25.10,OPED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1\fad(200,600)}{\blur2)}奇迹般闪耀的happy day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:07.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先看到的天空 是血的颜色
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.79,0:00:12.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最先嗅到的 是血的气味
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.74,0:00:22.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀人与被杀的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.81,0:00:41.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永不会醒来的噩梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.21,0:00:50.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 不让我安眠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:53.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.21,0:00:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又没吃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:00.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他人都像饿急了的猪一样狼吞虎咽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.37,0:01:02.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随你便了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.67,0:01:07.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:40.14,Title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,500)}{\blur3}魔剑 -Sword-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:46.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做阿丽亚 请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.99,0:02:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.56,0:02:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的任务就拜托你了 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.85,0:02:54.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么…要我护卫的货物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.37,0:03:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,汉尼拔 你没说明吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.46,0:03:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为这样比较有意思
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.45,0:03:07.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真恶趣味呢 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.76,0:03:11.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要保护的 就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.16,0:03:15.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我不是要保护魔剑吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.91,0:03:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.10,0:03:27.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后呢 这和你来我家有什么关系？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.36,0:03:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克 很遗憾 今天不是来找你的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:35.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点都不遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.51,0:03:38.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈哈 你真会开玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.81,0:03:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和笨骑士没什么家常可聊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砍了你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.60,0:03:48.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.02,0:03:50.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我 他们是恋人吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.53,0:03:58.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的名誉正面临被玷污的危机 快去否认
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.24,0:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到这种场景还认为是恋人的话 我倒想见见那人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝配
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.35,0:04:08.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.13,0:04:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少废话快去否认
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:14.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这东西的灵体好丰富啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.93,0:04:19.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 香辛料里放入了在灰幕森林采摘的果实
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.12,0:04:25.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 这附近的灵体浓度真高
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.15,0:04:28.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我们来说的确难得
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:37.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 这个女人哪里像魔剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.88,0:04:41.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 理所应当的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.20,0:04:45.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.04,0:04:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「解开沉眠 寻求真实 风凝吾手」
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.25,0:04:58.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以弑神」
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.41,0:05:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变成剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.71,0:05:38.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 刚才是剑以人类的形态出现
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:41.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这确实罕见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.83,0:05:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是魔剑阿丽亚 既是人也是剑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.75,0:05:50.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.98,0:05:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔剑生风
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.86,0:06:01.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才的 不是使用「祈祷契约」产生的风吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:07.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 发动「祈祷契约」需要玉钢作为触媒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.28,0:06:11.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是那柄细剑并非用玉钢制成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:14.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧见多识广
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.95,0:06:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凭空生风 寄宿着未知力量的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:20.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然剑如其名
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.19,0:06:22.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 可以了 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.89,0:06:37.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.10,0:06:40.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过 魔剑可是各国争红了眼的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.43,0:06:43.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然会把它交给你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人会想到魔剑化作人形四处走动
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.39,0:06:50.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 护卫越少越好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.12,0:06:53.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果还是女性 就更合适了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说出去的话呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.08,0:06:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会那么做的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么你们今天是来干什么的？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.21,0:07:06.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 找利萨有点事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:13.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌人一定会为魔剑卷土重来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.01,0:07:19.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且极有可能在市内施展恶魔契约
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样的话 在场各位中难免有人牺牲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们早有觉悟
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记住一点
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:36.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬畏死亡 并与死亡抗争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.95,0:07:40.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这会成为对抗恶魔时的最重要的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.46,0:07:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们面前的老头子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.33,0:07:49.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这样从上次战争中活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来 安排警卫配置
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.01,0:07:57.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长 在这之前
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:58.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.58,0:08:03.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么把魔剑交给塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.58,0:08:07.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是坎贝尔家的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:10.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不会辜负我的期望
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.96,0:08:21.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开了吃 放开了喝 别客气
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.37,0:08:23.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:25.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满嘴溢香
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.78,0:08:27.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来三人份的串烧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.94,0:08:30.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 芋头丸子和蜂蜜果
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.00,0:08:32.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.85,0:08:36.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来三人份的串烧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.38,0:08:40.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 连我也一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 经费全部报销 别担心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.22,0:08:49.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我跟团长说 想尝遍这里的美食
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.87,0:08:53.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我对这方面少有见识
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:55.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利萨能来 真是帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.76,0:08:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家店太正宗了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.61,0:09:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,量又多 又好吃 无可挑剔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.74,0:09:06.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的 我也很早就想来一次了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉汁好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.53,0:09:17.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太急小心噎着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:24.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 那个不争气的连饭都不让你吃饱吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:32.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来 卢克下周会去集市吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.12,0:09:35.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 卢克也去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.23,0:09:38.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 利萨一定很期待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.45,0:09:41.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 虽然每次都去集市
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.08,0:09:43.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但并不是去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:47.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢克为找一样东西
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.12,0:09:50.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 可以弑神的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.42,0:09:58.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 刚才的 刚才的当我没说
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神 杀神 不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.07,0:10:05.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是把厉害到几乎可以杀神的剑…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.28,0:10:12.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再来份芋头丸子 还有野鸟串烧也来份
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.67,0:10:20.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,风之魔剑 阿丽亚吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.60,0:10:22.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「以弑神」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.26,0:10:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那女人多半…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.05,0:10:30.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢 还是要讲缘分的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.72,0:10:32.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人也好 剑也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.21,0:10:38.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 来杯茶… 对了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.45,0:10:52.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座城市不错呢 治安也好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.06,0:10:55.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关键是没有死人的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.04,0:10:59.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然了 城市里怎么会有那种味道
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.28,0:11:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有那种城市哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.56,0:11:08.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尸体多过活人的街道 并不少见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.22,0:11:13.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为从前开始 我辗转过不少人手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.38,0:11:21.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.78,0:11:25.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.32,0:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:32.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.54,0:11:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚 你究竟…多大了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 40到50之间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,40…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:46.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概差不多吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.76,0:11:50.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我苏醒在瓦尔巴尼尔战争时期
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.44,0:11:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是在战场上
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接以剑的形态
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.09,0:12:00.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么身在那里 又是谁把我带到那里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.49,0:12:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.15,0:12:21.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是风之魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.35,0:12:26.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人们得知后 为争夺我杀红了眼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.57,0:12:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同野兽一般
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.77,0:12:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,许多人死去 死在我这把剑下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.71,0:12:42.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.68,0:12:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好悲惨的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.22,0:12:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睁开眼就在夺人性命 直到现在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.98,0:12:54.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是被迫去夺走才对 阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底什么是魔剑？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.47,0:12:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那当然是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.56,0:13:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.36,0:13:05.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 毫无疑问那是伤害别人的工具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.82,0:13:08.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我就是剑 是魔剑
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.34,0:13:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.66,0:13:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 对不起 原本没打算说这些
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.54,0:13:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的是 这个城市很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.93,0:13:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了塞西莉你们的保护
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.71,0:13:23.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的话 真想一直留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.05,0:13:25.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,务必要留在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.60,0:13:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定会保护阿丽亚的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.58,0:13:31.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 就留在这里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:35.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.02,0:14:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.89,0:14:10.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.49,0:14:11.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.97,0:14:17.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比通常用的小了一圈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.71,0:14:19.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该会比较好使
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.45,0:14:26.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很少见的形状呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Falseedge吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:27.90,test,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}假边
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.26,0:14:32.90,test,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs30}假边:无刃的刀边，为提高刺人时的贯穿力，剑身上的凹槽用来放血，并略微减轻剑重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是利萨
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.17,0:14:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不仅可以用来挥砍 还可以刺和突
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.80,0:14:34.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.00,0:14:38.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先练好挥砍的基本功如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.85,0:14:39.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷金纳德先生
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕蒂 我的剑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.62,0:14:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:46.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想说什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.72,0:14:50.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身手不跟上的话 拿着宝贝也浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.23,0:14:54.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 所以才不得不依赖精巧的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.74,0:14:56.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好没风度的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.71,0:14:58.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是毫不客气啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请 这是Zweihander
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:04.18,test,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs38}{\pos(700,660)}巨型双手剑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.98,0:15:10.18,test,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}{\fs30}巨型双手剑:16世纪神圣罗马帝国马克西米利安1世时代德国佣兵使用的巨型双手剑， 长1.8米重2.8-5kg，常在战场上用来斩断长矛的枪柄为骑兵开辟道路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.58,0:15:05.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.64,0:15:11.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑是杀人工具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.51,0:15:19.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只为砍杀眼前的敌人 没有其他意义
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.46,0:15:21.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那是不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,骑士的剑是保护市民的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.38,0:15:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剑就是剑 不过是武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.74,0:15:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这样的男人 我再熟悉不过了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只知砍砍杀杀 夺人性命
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.57,0:15:36.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认为“剑只要这样就好”
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的前任主人就是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.97,0:15:41.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.31,0:15:44.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了 满心绝望地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.98,0:16:14.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二小队前往东区 第四小队前往西区
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦发现黑衣男子 绝对不要放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.53,0:16:19.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.22,0:16:23.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下团长 我也要出动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.96,0:16:25.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 你留下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.12,0:16:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 只有我一人在安全的地方待命…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.73,0:16:32.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的任务是魔剑的护卫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.17,0:17:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.34,0:17:05.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.74,0:17:10.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.15,0:17:12.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,团长 那是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.73,0:17:15.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上次的战争中出现过的特殊虫类
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.29,0:17:17.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让它钻进体内的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.00,0:17:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就会被入侵大脑 成为被操纵的人偶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.22,0:17:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不得已了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.40,0:17:28.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个也别放跑
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.82,0:17:29.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.56,0:17:39.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有囚犯都误食了虫子 这样未免牵强啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:48.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣男子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:55.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.89,0:17:59.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 放心
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.20,0:18:01.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当然明白自己的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.01,0:18:03.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.55,0:18:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉的工作 是保护这座城市吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.83,0:18:12.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“可以一直留在这里”你说过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,留在塞西莉你们保护的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.20,0:18:17.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座没有死亡气味的城市
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.07,0:18:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别掉以轻心
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.73,0:18:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.63,0:19:06.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.24,0:19:13.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣男人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.95,0:19:17.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.67,0:19:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:28.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.28,0:19:32.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被虫子操纵了 是活死人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被虫子…那他也是牺牲者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.56,0:19:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以这么说…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.38,0:19:39.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救他的方法呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.89,0:19:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.96,0:19:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦成为那样 只有赐他一死
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:19:59.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别害怕 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:12.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在等什么 塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.63,0:20:18.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危险…卢克
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:20.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉 快砍下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:23.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.95,0:20:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:30.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么能对这个生命下手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.86,0:20:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…没有杀过人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.78,0:20:41.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 塞西莉{\fnsimhei}·{\r}坎贝尔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.56,0:20:43.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快砍
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.69,0:20:56.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个胆小鬼 趁早别当什么骑士了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.24,0:21:01.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.17,0:21:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 没有改变
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.85,0:21:07.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还以为多了些战斗的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.38,0:21:10.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞西莉
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.22,0:21:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是无可救药的好人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不知道 还有这么害怕夺人性命的骑士
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.67,0:21:27.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,长生不老也有好处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.10,0:21:31.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.14,0:21:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.16,0:21:38.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么我得不到救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:41.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你与恶魔缔结契约
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.13,0:21:44.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场战争中幸存下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.69,0:21:46.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为此牺牲了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.14,0:21:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我会拯救你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.38,0:21:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.00,0:21:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在寻找你这样的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.70,0:21:57.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够从地狱中存活下来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.03,0:22:01.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却无法摆脱地狱折磨的人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.36,0:22:05.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会给予你救赎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.58,0:22:09.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用你的灵魂做为交换
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.72,0:23:37.80,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}{\an8}制作：风中风铃 晶晶电脑 天国尘埃 安静の云
